# GameNative — Intelligent Game Settings System

## Overview

This builds a full Game Settings screen that looks and works like the
GameHub settings UI shown in the reference screenshots, but with smarter
logic. The screen has a LEFT SIDEBAR with categories and a RIGHT PANEL
showing settings for the selected category.

When a game cannot run due to hardware limitations, show a clear
compatibility warning with specific reasons and suggestions — never
let the user launch into a black screen crash without explanation.

